			<d2p1:Key>Description</d2p1:Key>
			<d2p1:Value xmlns:d4p1="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" i:type="d4p1:string">Simplified Management of Business Endpoint Security</d2p1:Value>
		</d2p1:KeyValueOfstringanyType>
		<d2p1:KeyValueOfstringanyType>
			<d2p1:Key>Overview</d2p1:Key>
			<d2p1:Value xmlns:d4p1="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" i:type="d4p1:string">&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="font-size: 18px; color: #0e77d9;"&gt;AhnLab Policy Center (APC) is a unified central management solution for managing our award-winning security applications for desktops and servers. From one location, easily manage and administer your endpoint security products to ensure seamless protection across the organization. APC provides flexible and scalable network configurations to fit any organization or network topology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style="padding: 35px 0px 35px 0px;"&gt;&lt;img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/Cms_Data/Contents/Ahnlab/Media/product/GL2.1.3_01_01.jpg" alt="GL2.1.3_01_01.jpg" height="722" width="750" /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;</d2p1:Value>
		</d2p1:KeyValueOfstringanyType>
		<d2p1:KeyValueOfstringanyType>
			<d2p1:Key>Features</d2p1:Key>
			<d2p1:Value xmlns:d4p1="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" i:type="d4p1:string">&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="font-size: 25px; color: #282828; padding-bottom: 15px;"&gt;Endpoint Protection&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="font-size: 18px; color: #282828; padding-bottom: 5px;"&gt;Security Policy Management&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;APC provides total virus and malware protection, by collaborating with all AhnLab V3 products in your network. With a fully-integrated console, administrators can easily configure and deploy security protection profiles for managed domains or groups.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="font-size: 18px; color: #282828; padding: 20px 0px 5px 0px;"&gt;Proactive Defense&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;APC detects system security vulnerabilities in advance, including unknown security threats, by analyzing the following behaviors: (1) vulnerable shared folders or user accounts detected, (2) infected agent computer detected, or (3) an agent computer that violates the internet access control policies of AhnLab TrusGuard.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="font-size: 25px; color: #282828; padding: 30px 0px 15px 0px;"&gt;Central Management&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="font-size: 18px; color: #282828; padding-bottom: 5px;"&gt;Administrative Console&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The single-point console lets administrators easily assess the security status of computers and servers across an entire corporate network. Administrators can configure settings, deploy APC agents, and control agent computers remotely.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="font-size: 18px; color: #282828; padding: 20px 0px 5px 0px;"&gt;Desktop Management&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This feature configures settings for endpoint security program patches, Windows updates, and power management for agent computers to keep all the computers in your network up-to-date and to reduce energy consumption. Remote control support enables quick technical support and troubleshooting of networked computers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="font-size: 18px; color: #282828; padding: 20px 0px 5px 0px;"&gt;Domain and Group Management&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;APC allows administrators to configure a domain or group based on internal organizational structures or other criteria. Simplified management of domains and groups provides effective control for large-scale networks and customizable security policies for each unit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="font-size: 25px; color: #282828; padding: 30px 0px 15px 0px;"&gt;Monitoring &amp;amp; Reporting&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="font-size: 18px; color: #282828; padding-bottom: 5px;"&gt;Dashboard&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The dashboard provides useful, at-a-glance information about your security status, including agent computer details, vulnerabilities, virus and spyware data, policy deployment, and scheduled tasks. Administrators can send notices, run engine updates, remotely control agent computers, distribute package files, run virus scans, or restart agents directly from the dashboard.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="font-size: 18px; color: #282828; padding: 20px 0px 5px 0px;"&gt;Reports&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;APC provides details about agent computers, including software and hardware configurations, vulnerable accounts and shared folders, security programs, and detected threats. Administrator can create custom reports with need-based queries and schedule reports at specified times.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style="padding: 35px 0px 35px 0px;"&gt;&lt;img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/Cms_Data/Contents/Ahnlab/Media/product/GL2.1.3_02_01.jpg" alt="GL2.1.3_02_01.jpg" height="724" width="760" /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;</d2p1:Value>
		</d2p1:KeyValueOfstringanyType>
		<d2p1:KeyValueOfstringanyType>
			<d2p1:Key>Advantages</d2p1:Key>
			<d2p1:Value xmlns:d4p1="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" i:type="d4p1:string">&lt;p style="font-size: 18px; color: #282828; padding-bottom: 5px;"&gt;Save Management costs&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px;"&gt;
&lt;li style="text-indent: -10px;"&gt;- With centralized management, you can reduce the overall costs needed to manage the security of all PCs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style="text-indent: -10px;"&gt;- By promptly applying PC management and policies to prevent malicious codes you can maximize operational efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style="text-indent: -10px;"&gt;- The cost and time required for PC security management can be reduced&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style="font-size: 18px; color: #282828; padding: 20px 0px 5px 0px;"&gt;Enhance Productivity&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;- By establishing a safe business security environment, you can enhance your business productivity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;- Security problems and accidents due to poor security consciousness of users can be prevented&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;- When PC problems occur, you can quickly get back to your work through central control&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style="font-size: 18px; color: #282828; padding: 20px 0px 5px 0px;"&gt;Flexibility Improve Image&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;- You can improve your company&amp;rsquo;s image as a reliable company by establishing a safe security environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;- You can secure competitiveness by managing stable operations of IT systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</d2p1:Value>
